OL,3,CFire breaks out a former convent in Co
OL,4,CDown
OL,6,FA major fire has broken out in
OL,7,FDownpatrick at a former convent.
OL,9,FThe alarm was raised at around 7pm on
OL,10,FSunday at the building on St Patrick's
OL,11,FAvenue, sparking a major Fire Service
OL,12,Fresponse.
OL,14,FEight appliances were at the scene on
OL,15,FSunday evening from Belfast, Lisburn
OL,16,Fand Comber. There was concerns in the
OL,17,Farea the fire could spread to the
OL,18,Fnearby parochial house and St
OL,19,FPatrick's chapel.
